---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Alex">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-stone-900 mb-6">About</h1>
  <div class="space-y-6 text-stone-600 leading-relaxed text-base">
    <p>
      I focus on stripping away complexity in web design. Overly designed sites slow down interfaces and obfuscate written messages.
    </p>
    <p>
      This platform serves as an open workspace where I share discoveries regarding interface programming, data integrity, and minimalism.
    </p>
    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-stone-900 mt-12 mb-3">Core Stack</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-sm text-stone-600">
      <li><strong>SSG:</strong> Astro (Static HTML Content Delivery)</li>
      <li><strong>Styling Engine:</strong> Tailwind CSS v4</li>
      <li><strong>Typography:</strong> Tailwind Prose Architecture</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>